I was curious about the performance, so I added a local benchmark (I don't think we should commit this, though). I was expecting the new version to perform better:

<details><summary>PrevectorEqualScriptMix</summary>


```patch
diff --git a/src/bench/prevector.cpp b/src/bench/prevector.cpp
--- a/src/bench/prevector.cpp	(revision 01dcb2fcc5834071eb3cc1c1ad2f8c931d80e741)
+++ b/src/bench/prevector.cpp	(revision 61567d548957ea3167088347b9db8332102522d1)
@@ -5,11 +5,16 @@
 #include <prevector.h>

 #include <bench/bench.h>
